Class Frame

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.qos.frame.Frame
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, NotPersistable, VariableEvaluator, UniqueObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataFrame, PrototypeFrame
public abstract class Frame
extends java.lang.Object
implements UniqueObject, java.lang.Cloneable, VariableEvaluator, NotPersistable

This class is the most abstract representation of a frame and includes almost all of the generic implementation.
